name: testNavigateToBuildPageFromTimeline
description: Verify the ability to navigate to build page of Freestyle, Pipeline and Multiconfiguration(not default) from timeline
descriptionHtml: Verify the ability to navigate to build page of Freestyle, Pipeline and Multiconfiguration(not default) from timeline

testStage.description: Verify the ability to navigate to build page of Freestyle, Pipeline and Multiconfiguration(not default) from timeline

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click 'Build History' on the side menu
Click last not default build link badge on the Jenkins table
Click last not default build link badge on bubble pop up from timeline
